715057f-a.title: Manhattan: 113th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
715057f-a.text:
228-230 East 113th Street, south side, between Second and Third
Aves. View shows Our Lady Queen of Angels R.C. Church.
October 17, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

707962f-b.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 113th Street
707962f-b.text:
(1)
2196 Second Avenue, adjoining the S.E. corner of 113th Street,
a three-story frame house.
October 17, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, two years earlier.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 25o.
CREDIT LINE IMPERaTIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
